posts.message:
I'm a long time reader of this group. Though I'm not Egyptian, I spend a lot of time in Cairo and I enjoy following along and learning about types of problems that devs are working on.

I'm trying to map out the online startup communities in Egypt so we can start figuring out how dopay can be most helpful for the startup ecosystem. I'd be super grateful if you could share any online groups that you read or post to. 

Thanks!
